2.3 Database Schema (from DBMS Practicals)
The existing Vehicle Rental Service schema is reused directly. Core tables:
▸	Customer (customer_id, name, contact, email, license_no)
▸	Vehicle (vehicle_id, type, model, brand, price_per_day, status)
▸	Supplier (supplier_id, company_name, location, verified, rating)
▸	Booking (booking_id, customer_id, supplier_id, vehicle_id, start_date, end_date, total_cost, status)
▸	Fleet (fleet_id, supplier_id, vehicle_id, available_count)
 
