User Booking Screen (Map View)
▸	Left panel: search bar, Vehicle Type dropdown, Date Range picker, Fleet Size filter
▸	Supplier list cards: thumbnail, company name, distance badge, vehicle count, price/day, star rating
▸	Right panel: Google Maps embed with orange location pins
▸	Map popup on pin click: company name, vehicle count, price/day, rating
▸	Sticky CTA: 'Book Selected Fleet' (full-width orange button)
Supplier Listing Screen
▸	Top filter bar: Location, Vehicle Type, Availability, Rating dropdowns
▸	3-column card grid: supplier photo, name, city, vehicle count, description excerpt, rating
▸	'Verified Supplier' green badge (top-right of card) for approved suppliers
